reviewText: I did get the movie, shipping was a little longer than I expected, but it came in and my kids are very happy! Some of the reviews say this is a fake, but I don't see how. All the shows are very clear, packaging was very nice, as was the covers. Happy customer!!
This is fake. Master Quest was part of the Johto Saga. The art work here is when Ash was in Hoenn, AFTER his time in Johto
Fun fact this is a illegal Malaysia DVD. Got a show called Zero No Tsukaima from the same place. Horrible quality and screams bootleg. Only buy if you want to make fun of it:)
